Number Pattern 1
Send Feedback
Print the following pattern for the given N number of rows.
Pattern for N = 4
1
11
111
1111
Input format :
Integer N (Total no. of rows)
Output format :
Pattern in N lines
Sample Input :
5
Sample Output :
1
11
111
1111
11111



# Read input as specified in the question.
## Print output as specified in the question.
n=int(input())
i=1
p=1
while i<=n:
    j=1
    while j<=i:
        print(p, end="")
        j=j+1
    print()
    i=i+1
